## Step-Back Analysis

Apply before creating content:

| Question | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| Goal? | Awareness / Consideration / Conversion / Retention |
| Audience? | Role, pain points, awareness level |
| Platform? | Telegram / LinkedIn / Instagram / Stories (TG/IG) |
| Main message? | ONE idea to remember |
| Hook? | Fact / Pain / Contradiction / Question |
| Proof? | Data, case study, example |
| CTA? | Specific action reader must take |

**MANDATORY**: Agree with user on answers to these questions before proceeding to next steps.

