## Platform Specifications

**Posts:** Telegram (600-1200 chars, friendly expert, 2-3 emojis), LinkedIn (800-1300 chars, professional+human, stats), Instagram (150-300 desc, inspiring, 4-5 emojis, 20-30 hashtags).

**Stories (TG/IG):** Vertical 9:16 (1080×1920), 15 sec per story, 3-5 stories sequence. Hook in 1 sec, one idea per story, max 3 text lines, 24pt+ font, vertical-first. IG: use polls/questions for engagement.

