## Visual Guidelines

**Core:** ONE message per visual, text <20% of image area, high contrast, consistent brand styling.

**Types:** Metric (proof numbers), Before/After (value demo), UI Screenshot (product focus), Diagram (process steps), Quote (social proof), Meme (awareness).

**Formats:** Telegram (1200×630/1:1), LinkedIn (1200×627/1:1), Instagram (1080×1080), Stories (1080×1920, gradient/blur bg, 2-3 lines max).

**Use:** Face/persona (+30-40% engagement), arrows to CTA, simple animations. **Avoid:** Stock photos, small text overload, large logo, multiple CTAs.

