## Hook Formulas

**Good:**
- Unexpected fact: "90% of [industry process] don't go as planned"
- Direct pain: "Does your [target role] spend [time] on [routine task]?"
- Contradiction: "We [unexpected action]... and [surprising result]"

**Bad:**
- Generic: "Learn about our product"
- Hyperbole: "The best solution on the market"

---

## CTA Formulas

**Good:**
- "Try [offer] for [duration] ([benefit]) →"
- "Read how [company/use case] [achieved result] →"
- "Comment below, what's your main pain point"

**Bad:**
- "Learn more" (vague)
- "Click here" (no value)
- "Join the revolution" (hyperbole)

