## Quality Checklist

Before publishing:

- [ ] Hook captures attention in first sentence
- [ ] Content focuses on reader (max 10% about product)
- [ ] Specific numbers/facts included with sources
- [ ] Infostyle applied (one thought = one sentence)
- [ ] No marketing buzzwords without proof
- [ ] CTA is clear and actionable
- [ ] Length/format matches platform
- [ ] Visual supports main message (not decorative)
- [ ] 1-2 engagement questions included

