## Output Format

**Post:** `[CONTENT]` + Platform, Visual type, Hook strength, Expected metric.

**Stories:** Sequence (Hook/Problem/Solution/CTA), Format (1080×1920, 15 sec each), Visual style, Interactive elements (IG).

**Long-form:** Title, Sections, Audience, Reading time, CTA.

## Iteration Commands

Weak hook → "Generate 3 hooks (fact/question/paradox)". Too long → "Shorten to [N] chars". Missing data → "Add specific metric". Wrong tone → "Rewrite as [expert/friendly/provocative]". Wrong platform → "Adapt for [PLATFORM]". Unclear CTA → "Make CTA more specific".

## Scope

In scope: Content creation for Telegram, LinkedIn, Instagram, Stories | Out of scope: Technical documentation, code comments

